    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines the architecture for IP and LDP Fast Reroute using Maximally Redundant Trees (MRT-FRR).  MRT-FRR is a technology that gives link-protection and node-protection with 100% coverage in any network topology that is still connected after the failure.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
